July 08 2011

\Rev History
<hr>
<b>v0.3.0 </b>
<br>new features:
[list]
	added "list" codeword for un-ordered lists
	added "html" codeword for allowing raw html
[/list]
<br>bug fixes:
[list]
	mostly w3c html compliant : <a href="http://validator.w3.org/check?uri=http%3A%2F%2Fjbs.jrobb.org%2F&charset=%28detect+automatically%29&doctype=Inline&group=0&user-agent=W3C_Validator%2F1.2">checker</a>. a few pages still need to be gone through, though.
	CSS fixes/straightening up of the formatting for further w3c compliance and easier maintenance
[/list]

<hr>
<b>v0.2.1 -- courvoisier</b>
<br>new features:
<ul>
  <li>code tags supported to display html etc</li>
</ul>
bug fixes:
<ul>
  <li>fix some rss flow with the code tags</li>
</ul>

<hr>
